Introduction

Kitten Girls (Korean: 키튼걸스) was a three-member girl group under Stone Entertainment, Wannabe Academy's Entertainment branch. They officially debuted on September 4, 2018, with the single "U Me Us". They unfortunately silently disbanded in late 2018.
